overview.en: LAS is committed to using the blockchain technology innovation field to serve entry-level application scenarios such as game finance, and actively expand global business with a brand-new token economic model and value return.
overview.zh: LAS致力于通过区块链科技创新领域为入口服务游戏金融等落地应用场景，用全新的通证经济模式和价值回报积极拓展全球业务。
